doc.after: The Shrine is managed by the Shrine of Remembrance Trustees ten individuals appointed by the Governor in Council on the advice of the Minister for Veterans Affairs in the Victorian Government 76 The Trustees are responsible for the care management maintenance and preservation of the Shrine and Shrine Reserve 76
